OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1772216417
OL,3,CFuture of Leonardo helicopter factory
OL,4,Cclose to being secured with major
OL,5,Ccontract
OL,7,FThe future of the Leonardo helicopter
OL,8,Ffactory in Yeovil looks close to being
OL,9,Fsecured with reports the Government is
OL,10,Fset to award it a new #1 billion
OL,11,Fcontract.
OL,13,FThousands of jobs have been under
OL,14,Fthreat after a decision on the
OL,15,Fcontract to build 23 defence
OL,16,Fhelicopters was delayed.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1772216417
OL,3,CFuture of Leonardo helicopter factory
OL,4,Cclose to being secured with major
OL,5,Ccontract
OL,7,FThe Government looks set to award that
OL,8,F#1 billion pound purchase of military
OL,9,Fhelicopters from Leonardo in Yeovil,
OL,10,Fwhich is this country's only
OL,11,Fspecialist factory, although the
OL,12,FMinistry of Defence is stressing the
OL,13,Fdeal is not yet finalised.
OL,15,FThe plant had been left in limbo by
OL,16,Fmonths of delays and there had been
OL,17,Fprotests from workers, worried that
OL,18,Fthe future of the factory, and their
OL,19,Fjobs, were under threat.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1772216417
OL,3,CFuture of Leonardo helicopter factory
OL,4,Cclose to being secured with major
OL,5,Ccontract
OL,7,FMultiple sources are speculating that
OL,8,Fa deal to build a fleet of 23 defence
OL,9,Fhelicopters will be signed off, with
OL,10,FUnite the union claiming a 'tremendous
OL,11,Fvictory' although questioning why the
OL,12,Fdecision wasn't made earlier.
OL,14,FThe Leonardo site employs 3,000
OL,15,Fworkers and was the only remaining
OL,16,Fbidder for the contract which has a
OL,17,Fdeadline on March 1st
OL,19,FThis Yeovil factory dates back to 1915
OL,20,Fwhen it built planes for use in World
OL,21,FWar One under the name Westland.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1772216417
OL,3,CFuture of Leonardo helicopter factory
OL,4,Cclose to being secured with major
OL,5,Ccontract
OL,7,FAs well as the 3,000 employed on site,
OL,8,Fa further 9,000 supply chain jobs are
OL,9,Fsupported locally by the factory, so
OL,10,Fthis increasing positivity will come
OL,11,Fas a big relief for the whole area.
OL,13,FYeovil MP Adam Dance said: "There has
OL,14,Fbeen positive progress on the New
OL,15,FMedium Helicopter contract in recent
OL,16,Fdays, and discussions are moving in a
OL,17,Fpromising direction. However, my
OL,18,Funderstanding is that nothing is
OL,19,Fformally agreed yet and the contract
OL,20,Fis not over the line.
OL,26,@uD@\OU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1772216417
OL,3,CFuture of Leonardo helicopter factory
OL,4,Cclose to being secured with major
OL,5,Ccontract
OL,7,F"I know how important this decision is
OL,8,Ffor Yeovil - for the workforce at
OL,9,FLeonardo, for the supply chain, and
OL,10,Ffor our town more widely. That is why
OL,11,FI have continuously pressing Ministers
OL,12,Ffor clarity and urgency and championed
OL,13,Fthis in Parliament.
OL,15,F"I remain cautiously optimistic and
OL,16,Fhope we will have more concrete news
OL,17,Fin the coming days. Until then, I will
OL,18,Fcontinue working behind the scenes to
OL,19,Fsecure the outcome Yeovil deserves."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU{D@dO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1772216417
OL,3,CFuture of Leonardo helicopter factory
OL,4,Cclose to being secured with major
OL,5,Ccontract
OL,7,FIt is understood Chancellor Rachel
OL,8,FReeves and Sir Keir Starmer had chosen
OL,9,Fto intervene in response to the
OL,10,FMinistry of Defence deprioritising the
OL,11,Fproject as part of the Defence
OL,12,FInvestment Plan.
OL,14,FA Treasury source said: "Rachel cares
OL,15,Fabout keeping the country safe and
OL,16,Fdriving jobs in the UK because our
OL,17,Fsecurity and economic growth are
OL,18,Ffundamentally connected.
OL,26,@vD@YOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1772216417
OL,3,CFuture of Leonardo helicopter factory
OL,4,Cclose to being secured with major
OL,5,Ccontract
OL,7,F"This project is key to those
OL,8,Fprinciples ` she wasn't going to let
OL,9,Fthis deal collapse under her watch."
OL,11,FTrade union Unite, which represents
OL,12,Fthousands of aerospace and defence
OL,13,Fworkers, said it was a "tremendous
OL,14,Fvictory" for the industry, the company
OL,15,Fand its staff that a contract was
OL,16,Fbeing awarded.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@dO]uD@XOUvD@HO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1772216417
OL,3,CFuture of Leonardo helicopter factory
OL,4,Cclose to being secured with major
OL,5,Ccontract
OL,7,FGeneral secretary Sharon Graham said:
OL,8,F"Unite has been campaigning for this
OL,9,FGovernment to buy British defence for
OL,10,Fover a year because it is vital for
OL,11,Fjobs and skills as well as national
OL,12,Fsecurity.
OL,14,F"The Leonardo contract is a tremendous
OL,15,Fvictory for Unite members in Yeovil
OL,16,Fand across the aerospace sector.J"Of
OL,17,Fcourse, we are pleased that Rachel
OL,18,FReeves has now listened to Unite on
OL,19,Fthis issue.
OL,26,@pD@AOUvD@AOUxD@bOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1772216417
OL,3,CFuture of Leonardo helicopter factory
OL,4,Cclose to being secured with major
OL,5,Ccontract
OL,7,F"However, it took way too long to get
OL,8,Fthis done, and we still have to
OL,9,Fquestion why workers were left in the
OL,10,Fdark until the 11th hour."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
